These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, fisherman, teacher, pilot, scientist, musician, accountant
There are 7 different nationalities: british, indonesian, polish, egyptian, spanish, dutch, malaysian
 1. the pilot is on the left of the egyptian##1
 2. the spanish is the pilot##1
 3. the accountant is on the right of the musician##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the teacher is in the middle##1
 6. the british is on the far left##1
 7. the scientist is the british##1
 8. the librarian is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the indonesian##1
10. the egyptian is on the left of the teacher##1
11. the accountant is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | scientist | pilot | fisherman | teacher | librarian | musician | accountant |
| Nationality   | british    | spanish   | egyptian      | dutch | polish    | indonesian    | malaysian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: plum, pepper, avocado, lime, apricot, apple, radish
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: house, electronic, indie, classical, r&b, metal, disco
 1. the fan of r&b is the person eating lime##1
 2. the person eating apple is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 3. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 5. the person eating lime is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 6. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 7. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | plum | pepper | apricot | lime | apple | radish | avocado |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | indie   | classical   | r&b      | house       | disco       | metal     |

