.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: grapes, lime, peas, peach, nectarine, broccoli, artichoke
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, musician, librarian, electrician, chef, dressmaker, firefighter
 1. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the firefighter##1
 3. the musician is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the analyst is the person eating nectarine##1
 6. the librarian is on the right of the musician##1
 7. the musician is on the left of the librarian##1
 8. the musician is on the right of the electrician##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is the electrician##1
10. the person eating peas is on the right of the analyst##1
11. the electrician is in the middle##1
12. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | lime | nectarine     | peas  | broccoli       | grapes       | artichoke  | peach   |
| Job    | dressmaker  | analyst | firefighter | electrician | musician | librarian | chef |

