.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep, funk, reggae, country, trance, house
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, british, mexican, canadian, american, german, malaysian
 1. the fan of country is the british##1
 2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the german is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the italian is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the right of the german##1
 9. the fan of funk is the american##1
10. the american is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
11. the malaysian is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | house     | reggae     | funk      | dubstep | country      | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | canadian | mexican | german | american | malaysian | british | italian |

