.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, writing, baking, filmmaking, camping, hiking
7 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, cat, goat, lizard, rabbit, hamster
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | collecting | writing | camping     | baking | hiking | filmmaking | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | hamster   | cat    | lizard | rabbit     | bird         | goat     | ferret        |

