.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade, milk, tea
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, van, subway, motorbike, boat, car, roller
 1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | milk   | fanta | mirinda | tea  | lemonade | cola |
| Transport   | motorbike   | boat | airplane | car     | van | roller | subway   |

