.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, comedy, horror, superhero, spy, action
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, airplane, subway, car, bus, scooter, taxi
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the person watching action movies is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the van is the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | action | horror | superhero | spy     | thriller | comedy |
| Transport     | scooter | car      | taxi | subway    | bus | airplane   | van  |

