 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
