 7. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
